Package: tccquickr
Title: Experimental R-to-C Lowering on Top of 'Rtinycc'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Sounkou Mahamane",
      family = "Toure",
      email = "sounkoutoure@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides an experimental and intentionally narrow
    declare()-annotated R-to-C lowering pipeline built on top of
    'Rtinycc'. The package contains the parser, IR, lowering, and
    code-generation layers for the tcc_quick prototype while keeping the
    underlying TinyCC toolchain and FFI runtime in 'Rtinycc'
    <https://github.com/sounkou-bioinfo/Rtinycc>.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Depends: R (>= 4.4.0)
Imports:
    Rtinycc
Suggests:
    tinytest,
    quickr
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
URL: https://github.com/sounkou-bioinfo/tccquickr, https://sounkou-bioinfo.r-universe.dev/tccquickr, https://github.com/sounkou-bioinfo/Rtinycc
BugReports: https://github.com/sounkou-bioinfo/tccquickr/issues
